{"tid":705351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中綫再爆醜聞　田北辰：消息指會展站挖掘工程支撐不足","createTime":"2018-06-17T05:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T19:58:41.000Z","uid":17646,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2f7b3aae3804627c5aa6e206ed66f90b07560e","tid":705351,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中綫再有車站爆出懷疑施工問題。立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰稱收到消息，指會展站的承建商在挖掘工程中未有放置足夠橫向支撐，被港鐵勒令暫停挖掘。<br />\n<br />\n會展站工程由「禮頓&mdash;中建聯營」承建。《明報》及香港電台今日均引述田北辰表示接獲消息，指承建商在挖掘工程期間，應該要在垂直牆身之間放置橫向支撐物。但港鐵發現承建商在施工期間，疑未有放置足夠數目的橫向支撐物，被勒令暫停挖掘工程。<br />\n<br />\n「我收到消息指，有人沒有跟足程序做，漏了一、兩支（支撐物）還一直在挖。似乎港鐵捉到、看到，便立即喝停。」田北辰說未知現時工程狀況，又關注港鐵高層是否得悉事件。"},{"pid":"6f2e3265230471f4cf9a74e5ca053c8e93d0f4a6","tid":705351,"uid":27664,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"維修部：長做長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b0886a78f90e52d1105de72e6223254c8b9f4c","tid":705351,"uid":41658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"再叫立法會科水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8fa9ba44cc12731bec2e1f3c7d7494d97b8937","tid":705351,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e67053149f1a22a77cf1d6f4bf060c8f115c40","tid":705351,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"478f270632d9ca820302c75517df4bec11d0b9b8","tid":705351,"uid":41602,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"禮頓咪即係UGL"},{"pid":"18d5e97f5513398bcb56d1b463239322e2e1d0cf","tid":705351,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"一定係嗰3舊炸彈累事啦"},{"pid":"9e9387